  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Properness Actions for the Migrants Response in Yemen</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will enhance the preparedness of IOM to respond to the migrants&#x2019; needs in Yemen in a timely manner by enhancing the capacity of the local partners to support the multi-sectorial assistance for the migrants and to support the humanitarian evacuation; stockpiling life-saving materials and kits (including transit, hygiene and shelter kits); providing the needed multi -sectorial assistance like; shelter, water, food; supporting the land transportation for the migrants from the conflict areas to the safe areas inside Yemen; enhancing preparedness further by having a number of boats on standby in the international waters to evacuate the migrants who are willing to return from Yemen to their country of origin, via Djibouti.</narrative>
  </description>
